        "creation_date": 1289820669,
        "body": "<p>You've likely got an issue with foreign key constraints, see <a href=\"http://dev.mysql.com/doc/refman/5.1/en/innodb-foreign-key-constraints.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://dev.mysql.com/doc/refman/5.1/en/innodb-foreign-key-constraints.html<\/a> for more details.<\/p>\n\n<p>First one to check is whether your LOG_ID reference to T_AJPES_TR_LOG(ID_LOG) is correct<\/p>\n",
